st an hour to set up and can be controlled via an app on your phone. With this mower you can expect precision cutting, with its adjustable blades and cutting heights.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eAt just £199, the Aldi robot lawn mower is one of the cheapest models I’ve seen. If you’ve been wondering \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-advice/how-much-to-spend-on-a-lawn-mower\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-advice/how-much-to-spend-on-a-lawn-mower\"\u003e\u003cu\u003ehow much to spend on a lawn mower\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, experts typically recommend spending anything between £200 and £400, making this mower feel like a total steal.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe garden gadget claims to be hassle-free, keeping your garden in shape with minimal intervention from you. Controlled via app, which connects to the mower using a Bluetooth connection, you can sit back, relax and control the mower with your smartphone. You can even schedule the mower in advance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAldi states the lawn mower has a one-time setup, meaning it should be easy to connect every time you use it. It also comes with a charging station and clip-on cover for all weather protection.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-MEdVRc5LbzBC6C8HQk7GVD\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Aldi robot lawn mower has obstacle, tilt and turnover sensors so you don\u0026#39;t have to worry about it falling over on your lawn. Plus, it has a maximum slope of 30%, meaning you can still use it if your garden isn’t flat. It has been designed with adjustable cutting heights to mow grass from 20-55mm with precision in gardens up to 400m.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H.png\" alt=\"Aldi robot lawn mower on freshly cut grass.\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8weGtTrbU6G99xvhJVZi6H.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Aldi)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe f